JINJA 2

1. Python variables {{varibales}}
Eg:
<p>Welcome {{name}}</p>
It reduces repetition of code

2. Conditionals
{% if %}...{% endif %}
Eg:
{% if is_topper %}
<p>You are a topper</p>
{% else %}
<p>You need to work hard</p>
{% endif %}

make sure to use endif atlast and endfor if for loop is used
{% for subject in subjects %}
<li> {{subject}} </li>
{% endfor %}

